  "name": "Mor Deythan Squad",
  "titles": "Mor Deythan Squad",
  "lore": "Informally known as the ‘Shadow Masters’, the Mor Deythan are a small cadre of infiltration squads within a Legion already well known for its nigh unsurpassed skill in such tactics. At the beginning of the Horus Heresy, the Mor Deythan were few in number, having fought countless campaigns over eight decades at their master’s side, and they rarely admit new recruits into their ranks. Most who remain are grizzled veterans, supremely confident in their abilities. They are adept at moving silent and unseen through the shadows and attacking as and where they will, unleashing deadly accurate sniper fire upon their foes.",
